  - Similar layout / drawers / table / modal to your provided client/caisse file.
  - Expects pywebview API endpoints:
      window.pywebview.api.get_vols()
      window.pywebview.api.add_vol(payload)
      window.pywebview.api.update_vol(payload)
      window.pywebview.api.delete_vol(id)
